計數：

```python
words = ["蘋果", "香蕉", "蘋果", "橘子", "蘋果", "香蕉"]
count = {}
for w in words:
    count[w] = count.get(w, 0) + 1
print(count)  # {'蘋果': 3, '香蕉': 2, '橘子': 1}
```

對照表：

```python
grade_names = {"A": "優", "B": "良", "C": "及格", "F": "不及格"}
print(grade_names.get("A"))  # 優
```

```python
s = {1, 2, 2, 3, 3, 3}
print(s)        # {1, 2, 3}
print(2 in s)   # True

s.add(4)
s.remove(1)
print(s)  # {2, 3, 4}

# 集合運算
a = {1, 2, 3}
b = {2, 3, 4}
print(a | b)  # {1, 2, 3, 4} 聯集
print(a & b)  # {2, 3} 交集
print(a - b)  # {1} 差集
```
